Generic single-database async configuration with asyncpg.

Generate a migration:
    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://user:pass@host/edgepulse \
        alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"

Apply migrations:
    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://user:pass@host/edgepulse \
        alembic upgrade head

Rollback one step:
    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://user:pass@host/edgepulse \
        alembic downgrade -1
